Related: robot

Conversion kit retrofits typical dishwasher 4 slideout half trays.

Dirty dishes are loaded into 4 other trays stacked near the sink.

Dirty trays replace clean when wash finishes with no dish touched.

New cupboard buildouts could be designed to hold these same trays.

====Other names
RoboWash, DishBgone, washBgone, KitchAmatic

===Other ideas
InstaWash: Single item dish or clothes washer steam cleans then blows dry in seconds.

Direct-solar plus furnace buring woodchips from our yearly clippings gives low-tech, nearly free heat.

No-soap: Never touch soap again.  Container holds some gallons of liquid or powder dispensed at each wash.
